    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>44952</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_001_029_001&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ノームに襲われた時、飛んで逃げりゃよかったのに、
何してたんだよ？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Hey, remember back when we were about to finish Gnome? Why did he run away all of a sudden?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>45040</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_001_029_002&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>飛ぶためには色々準備が必要なんだよ？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Wasn't it obvious why he ran?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>45144</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_001_029_003&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>空気の流れに乗ったり、
羽根のコンディション見たりさ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>The air around him was damp and after sensing it he felt the need to run away.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>45216</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_001_029_004&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>そんなの初聞きたぜ？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>That's the first time I heard that.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>45312</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_001_029_005&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>いつも簡単に飛んでるように
見えるけど……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>His reasons seem to be simple, but...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>45432</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_001_029_006&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>これでもすごく気を使ってるんだ。
風が強かったりしたら、落ちるし……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>He was being very careful! If the wind had become strong, the ceiling would be crushe--...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>6</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>45500</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_001_029_007&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>クルクルール！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Kurukuruuuru!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>7</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>45600</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_001_029_008&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>うわっ！　ちょっ……
じゃれつかないでって……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Ahh! I don't want to play right now!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>8</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>45676</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_001_029_009&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>クルール！　クルール！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Kururu! Kururu!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>9</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>45796</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_001_029_010&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>わっ……ほら、あっと、ちょっと……
ほ、ほらね……うわっ、やめて……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>T-there...good boy...calm down...please...Wah! Please stop!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>10</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
